Package com.sun.appserv.management.config

The com.sun.appserv.management.config package contains all MBean interfaces for configuration MBeans.

Package com.sun.appserv.management.config Description

The com.sun.appserv.management.config package contains all MBean interfaces for configuration MBeans.
